title: Nobody wants war, says Kim Jong Un impersonator
text:
Nobody wants war, says Kim Jong Un impersonator Friday, February 09, 2018 - 01:16 
Two impersonators of U.S. President Donald Trump and North Kroean leader Kim Jong Un suprised people in downtown Seoul before the opening of Olympics. No reporter narration.
